               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310217-265-cd1535" type="crimeDate">15th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-265-off1534 t18310217-265-cd1535"></join>, 4 sheets, value 6s., and 3 bags, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18310217-265-victim2375" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Powell
                  <interp inst="t18310217-265-victim2375" type="surname" value="Powell"></interp>
